public Books.Myconfig.ReleaseDownloadAccess releaseDownloadAccess(List<String> volumeIds,
                                                                  String cpksver)
                                                           throws IOException
Release downloaded content access restriction. Create a request for the method "myconfig.releaseDownloadAccess". This request holds the parameters needed by the the books server. After setting any optional parameters, call the Books.Myconfig.ReleaseDownloadAccess.execute() method to invoke the remote operation.

Parameters:
volumeIds - The volume(s) to release restrictions for.
cpksver - The device/version ID from which to release the restriction.

Request concurrent and download access restrictions. Create a request for the method "myconfig.requestAccess". This request holds the parameters needed by the the books server.
